column3: “Grape Dawg from Nebula has wonderful grape flavor with the classic ‘dawg’ bud structure, I wouldn’t call this a daytime smoker but a wonderfully relaxing strain with some nice pain relief.”
“great indica dominated hybrid, nice grape taste. nice strain if ur having a lazy day”
“Good body buzz, not a cerebral or anxious high. Euphoric and a great night’s sleep after.”
